summary: This FBI 302 form documents TD Bank's response to a Federal Grand Jury subpoena from the Southern District of New York, dated August 27, 2019. The document is a record of financial records production related to the Epstein investigation, with no FBI recommendations or conclusions included.

keyFacts: TD Bank responded to a Federal Grand Jury subpoena from the Southern District of New York on August 27, 2019.
The FBI 302 form documenting this response was drafted on December 6, 2019, and entered into FBI records on December 9, 2039.
The document contains no FBI recommendations or conclusions and is restricted from distribution outside the receiving agency.
